(251, '', '', '', 'BatchLoad', 'Pre', 'BatchLoadPre_1', 'BatchLoad Process Validations - Status and Error ', NULL, 'Prerequiste:\n1.Add 10  US Customers(5 customers without the mandatory data),Contacts, contracts and relationships with the MinimumRequirement data from EBS into ETL staging tables tables\n\n', 'Add data into following tables\n1)Customer\n2)Contact\n3)Contract\n4)Address\n5)Holding\n5)Cust_to_Cont\n6)Cust_to_Hold\n7)Con_to_Hold\n', '1)The entities should be loaded successfully and  should persist in Source DB\n', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL),
(252, '', '', '', 'BatchLoad', NULL, 'BatchLoad_1', NULL, NULL, '1)Run ETL jobs to fetch the records from source to MDM\n2)Validate if the status is changed to IP_E from New when the job is in running status\n', 'Data added as part of prerequisite should persist in Source DB for below tables\n1)Customer\n2)Contact\n3)Contract\n4)Address\n5)Holding\n5)Cust_to_Cont\n6)Cust_to_Hold\n7)Con_to_Hold', '1)The processed_Status should be changed to IP_E  for below fields(during the processing time)\nCustomer.PROCESSED_STATUS = IP_E\nContact.PROCESSED_STATUS = IP_E\nAddress.PROCESSED_STATUS = IP_E\nCust_Contact_Rel.PROCESSED_STATUS = IP_E\nHolding.PROCESSED_STATUS = IP_E\nContract.PROCESSED_STATUS = IP_E\ncont_to_hold_rel.PROCESSED_STATUS = IP_E\ncust_to_hold_rel.PROCESSED_STATUS = IP_E\n2)ETL job status should be success', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'TDD 6.1.1 \nTDD 6.2.1', '', NULL),
(253, '', '', '', 'BatchLoad', NULL, 'BatchLoad_2', NULL, NULL, 'Validate if the status is changed to IP_M from IP_E and processed_status_date is changed to current time stamp', 'Data added as part of prerequisite should persist in Source DB for below tables\n1)Customer\n2)Contact\n3)Contract\n4)Address\n5)Holding\n5)Cust_to_Cont\n6)Cust_to_Hold\n7)Con_to_Hold', '1)The processed_Status should be changed to IP_M  for below tables\nCustomer -5\nContact -10\nAddress-10 \nCust_Contact_Rel -10\nHolding -10 \nContract -10\ncont_to_hold_rel -10\ncust_to_hold_rel -10\n 2)  PROCESSED_STATUS_DT should be populated with Current timestamp for below tables.\nCustomer\nContact\nAddress\nCust_Contact_Rel\nHolding\nContract\ncont_to_hold_rel\ncust_to_hold_rel\n\n', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'TDD 6.1.1 \nTDD 6.2.1', '', NULL),
(254, '', '', '', 'BatchLoad', NULL, 'BatchLoad_3', NULL, NULL, 'Validate if the status is changed to E_E from IP_E and processed_status_date is changed to current time stamp', 'Data added as part of prerequisite should persist in Source DB for below tables\n1)Customer\n2)Contact\n3)Contract\n4)Address\n5)Holding\n5)Cust_to_Cont\n6)Cust_to_Hold\n7)Con_to_Hold', '1)The processed_Status should be changed to E_E  for below tables\nCustomer -5\n 2)  PROCESSED_STATUS_DT should be populated with Current timestamp for below tables.\nCustomer\nContact\nAddress\nCust_Contact_Rel\nHolding\nContract\ncont_to_hold_rel\ncust_to_hold_rel\n\n', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'TDD 6.1.1 \nTDD 6.2.1', '', NULL),
(255, '', '', '', 'BatchLoad', NULL, 'BatchLoad_4', NULL, NULL, 'Validate the count of the records created in the batch file and name of the batchfile is created in expected format', 'Data added as part of prerequisite should persist in Source DB for below tables\n1)Customer\n2)Contact\n3)Contract\n4)Address\n5)Holding\n5)Cust_to_Cont\n6)Cust_to_Hold\n7)Con_to_Hold', '1)Batch file should be created for all the below tables with respective count\nCustomer -5\nContact -10\nAddress -10\nCust_Contact_Rel -10\nHolding -10\nContract -10\ncont_to_hold_rel -10\ncust_to_hold_rel -10\n 2)  The format of the batch file should be  Maintain_<Entity>_<batchno>_<TimeStamp>.txt\n3)Batch file should be created successfully for each entity(Customer,Contact,Contract) and the created date for  the entities should be in below order\ni)contract(latest)\nii)Contact\niii)Customer', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'TDD 6.1.1 \nTDD 6.2.1', '', NULL),
(256, '', '', '', 'BatchLoad', NULL, 'BatchLoad_5', NULL, NULL, 'Validate if the status of the records and error messages are being capured in CTRL_RUN table and Error_Log table\n', 'Data added as part of prerequisite should persist in Source DB for below tables\n1)Customer\n2)Contact\n3)Contract\n4)Address\n5)Holding\n5)Cust_to_Cont\n6)Cust_to_Hold\n7)Con_to_Hold', 'Below fields should be populated in CTRL table.\nCTRL_RUN.Batch_no(PK)\nCTRL_RUN.Entity\nCTRL_RUN.No.of.recs =30\nCTRL_RUN.ETL_Failure_Cnt =5\nCTRL_RUN.Total_Failed =5\nCTRL_RUN.Total_Success = 25\nCTRL_RUN.Start_time\nCTRL_RUN.End_time\n2) Error_log table should be populated with the failure count with respective error messages(5 entries) with primary key of entity table as Entity id', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'TDD 6.1.1 \nTDD 6.2.1', '', NULL),
