(540, '', '', '', 'FULL_CONT_ADDR', NULL, 'FULL_CONT_ADDR_1_Pre_a', 'MaintainParty - Add a  Contact with ,Contact Name, Role(Customer Relationship) & Email \n\n', NULL, 'prerequisite :\n1.Add a   Person Customer with minimum data requirement from EBS Account Number into the staging table\n2.Run the ETL job\n3.Ensure XML''s are generated successfully\n4.Run the batch processor to send batch loads to MDM\n5.Validate the data in the MDM Database\n6.Validate staging audit tables\n\n', 'Add a Entity with the following tables :\n\n\nCustomer : \ncreate_dt\ncust_First_Name\ncust_Last_Name\nMarket_Type ="Individual"\nSubmarket_Type\nEntity_Type = "NULL"\nEntity_Status\nSource_system = EBS\nEBS_Acct_Num\n\nAddress :\naddress_type\naddress_line_one\ncity_name\ncountry \nState\npostal_code', '1.Verify the XML''s generated by the ETL job\n2.The entity (Person) should be successfully created in the MDM  Database and Ensure MDM Generated  Enterprise Customer ID in Contequiv\nADMIN_CLIENT_ID\nADMIN_SYS_TP_CD = 1000010 \n3.Validate Whether the XPQ_ENTITY_TP_CD ="Customer" in Contact Table\n4.The following table fields should get populated with the corresponding input values \nPERSONNAME\ngiven_name_one\nlast_name\nCONTACT\nXPQ_cust_market_tp_cd\nXPQ_cust_submarket_tp_cd\nCLIENT_ST_TP_CD\nsource_ident_tp_cd\nADDRESSGROUP\naddr_usage_tp_cd\nADDRESS\naddr_line_one\ncity_name\ncountry_tp_cd\nContequiv\nADMIN_CLIENT_ID\nADMIN_SYS_TP_CD = 1000008', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
